Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:35.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:40.87,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你还能够说是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:46.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}崩坏的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:51.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:23:00.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何人的呼唤 幻化为耳鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:05.59,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}时间似乎静止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}啊 觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:13.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}冲破这无边的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:18.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}疾风一般逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:23.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾如行尸走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:30.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们 到城墙之外 再相见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:34.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在地图之外
