Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:09.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我们彻夜长谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:14.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}低矮的房屋不算坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:20.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}我们能够互通心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我们的光就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}把酒高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我们迎接明朝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:45.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我们生活在这尘烟弥漫的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}长夜漫漫
